div.p: Scenario: One epoll_wait batch contains multiple events for fd=7. Invariant: Modifications to the interest set must be deferred or guarded by a zombie flag.

g.text: **The Batch Snapshot**: The events array in user-space now contains TWO entries for fd=7.
**Race Window**: Another part of the app (e.g. accept4) now gets fd=7 for a NEW client.
